0.1.0
- initial version
- Druid background, hireable from the start, with a Summon Beast active
- beasts are chosen by the battlefield: wolves in snow, wolves/spiders on grassland,
  wolves/spiders/young schrats in forests, wolves/hyenas on steppe and hills,
  hyenas/snakes in the desert, spiders/snakes in swamps
- Druid-only perks: Apex Predators, Pack, Regrowth, Entangling Roots, Venom, Pack Leader
- Regrowth heals one ally per turn; only one ally can carry it at a time
- Proper Druid origin
- Russian localization (req Rosetta)
